Introduction:

	This is my first project, just a demo. If you have any suggestion or advice, please feel free to let me know.

Details:

	This is a communication tool at the local network. There are two different programs:
	* server	Accepting users login in and maintaining on-line table and their friends  
	* customer	Users use this to communicate with each other

# Server:
	
	* Maintaining users table and accepting users login in who are in the users table.
	* Maintaining On-line table and push them to whom has a friendship with them.

